{"tid":1989502,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"黃金周首錄零內地團","createTime":"2020-04-26T04:30:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-27T09:49:17.000Z","uid":81228,"like":53,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0e09c23d70a56d62e587a8f779458a151e2e521a","tid":1989502,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T04:30:53.000Z","msg":"近年黃金周已不再黃金，在反修例等事件後，內地客驟減，但黃金周近乎無內地客來港就是首次。去年受惠於高鐵及港珠澳大橋通車後，內地五˙一黃金周四天假期有近一百萬人次的內地客訪港，較前一年三日黃金周假期，多出六成六。<br />\n<br />\n不過，旅議會總幹事陳張樂怡表示，內地目前仍未放行跨省、長途及跨境遊，今年五˙一黃金周不會有內地團來港，但不排除有個別內地散客。入境處統計顯示，近日只有不足一百人次內地客入境，前日更只有四十人次。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>旅議會：最高峰每日300團</strong><br />\n<br />\n○三年沙士後，內地同年七月底推出「自由行」；之前本港只有四家旅行社可接待「團進團出」的內地團，及後自由行及內地購物團大增。至○七年八月，旅議會設立登記內地入境團制度，每日可多達三百團，至近年才回落到數十至一百團。不過今年五˙一黃金周，更首次錄得「零」內地團。"},{"pid":"054040b9a5031dc1242c0a1d2fe6796bfe893d79","tid":1989502,"uid":92500,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T04:54:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ff4119231db6d2bad257beeaf509f9d97c7cabdf","tid":1989502,"uid":42951,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T05:11:05.000Z","msg":"繼續上，唔好比佢停"},{"pid":"f4f86a6d6e9811c6128f751313bd82193d550789","tid":1989502,"uid":58453,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T05:15:21.000Z","msg":"好好呀 <br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">五一黃金周<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"7a7ca612cedee23326ac8e6e3dc7a4467e6f6dbc","tid":1989502,"uid":111316,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T05:16:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57ee0b953bc920fcbd2c5b3ae9773fe640ce0f89","tid":1989502,"uid":195136,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T05:17:32.000Z","msg":"香港又非典炎又武漢不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95ef0b2f06f84614c120f06a9549b9b1916469af","tid":1989502,"uid":37524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T05:19:14.000Z","msg":"下年可能無黃金周lu<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e31d34eeb9a8d02aca7368b0c2ffc0fb9b5cdfc9","tid":1989502,"uid":235278,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T06:08:33.000Z","msg":"我就係要呢d <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88dbcf27a07c384c0430784919d36905ec217c2d","tid":1989502,"uid":301952,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T06:14:00.000Z","msg":"P牌手動正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf205a77cac96dfdacd7c321269ab8f23e456c9e","tid":1989502,"uid":340081,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T06:30:33.000Z","msg":"好爽呀 耳根清靜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6e1265f8c6ecc46167e24a5a5e4a75959ecd1fc","tid":1989502,"uid":13308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T09:36:32.000Z","msg":"咁開心?值得慶祝"},{"pid":"614a888b6992693a18af23095e979a9302596c7a","tid":1989502,"uid":129664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T09:49:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">今年五˙一黃金周不會有內地團來港，但不排除有個別內地散客。</span><br />\n<br />\n點解會有支那散客？佢地唔係要隔離14日咩？得7日簽證散客點嚟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}